thread.title: Brendan Donnelly

author: Brendan Donnelly
title: Brendan Donnelly
text: I rang up approx.one month before my policy was due for renewal asking what I needed to do to move to another insurer once my policy ended, was told I needed to do nothing from my side which was correct but this should have been flagged that I was intending to leave and an effort made to find out why, no joined up thinking and no interest in keeping me as a customer
